ries regular\n|-\n| 2018|| ''[[Fighting Season]]'' || Sgt Sean Collins || Miniseries; 6 episodes\n|-\n|}\n\n==Personal life==\nJay Ryan and Dianna Fuemana had a daughter in 2013.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://celebritybabies.people.com/2013/07/31/jay-ryan-welcomes-daughter-eve/|title=Jay Ryan Welcomes Daughter Eve|date=August 2013|accessdate=31 July 2013|last=Leon|first=Anya|work=People Magazine}}</ref>\n\n==Awards==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"style=;\"width:2;\"| Year  \n! scope=\"col\" style=\"style=;\"width:2;\"| Award\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"style=;\"width:2;\"| Work  \n! scope=\"col\" style=\"style=;\"width:3%;\"| Result \n|-\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center\" |2003\n| [[Logie Awards of 2003|Logie Award]] for [[Logie Award for Most Popular New Male Talent|Most Popular New Male Talent]]\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center\" | ''[[Neighbours]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center\" |2014\n| [[Equity Ensemble Awards|Equity Ensemble Award for Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Miniseries or Telemovie]] \n| rowspan=1 style=\"text-align:center\" | ''[[Top of the Lake]]''\n| {{won}}\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Jay Ryan}}\n*{{Twitter}}\n*{{IMDb name|1216008|Jay Ryan}}\n* [http://tvnz.co.nz/go-girls/jay-ryan-plays-kevin-2446754 Jay Ryan page \u2013 Official Go Girls Website]\n\n{{EquityAward TVMiniSeriesTeleMovieCast 2010\u20132019}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Ryan, Jay}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:New Zealand male actors]]\n[[Category:1981 births]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2019}}\n{{Use New Zealand English|date=July 2019}}\n{{Infobox person\n|name          = Jay Ryan\n|image         = Jay Ryan by Gage Skidmore 2.jpg\n|imagesize     = \n|caption       = Ryan at the 2013 [[San Diego Comic-Con International|Comic-Con]] in San Diego\n|birthname     = \n|birth_date    = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1981|8|29}}